Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.74,0:23:18.31,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.79,0:23:22.79,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(524,1)}Sekke's Bah-Ha Seminar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.67,0:23:22.18,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Sekke's Bah-Ha Seminar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.13,0:23:24.29,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.29,0:23:26.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.93,0:23:26.54,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong! It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.54,0:23:27.80,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:29.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.64,0:23:33.30,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, you have yet to learn \Nthe ways of the bah-ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:34.80,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:36.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The ways of the bah-ha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.49,0:23:42.15,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! This is my chance \Nto make a name for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.15,0:23:46.18,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch the thief and \Nget praise from the Wizard King, ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.18,0:23:50.22,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 12:\N"The Wizard King Saw."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.48,0:23:55.00,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(196,1)}Page 10\N\N{\fs18}The Wizard King Saw
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.22,0:23:53.70,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up is my bah-ha!
